      int MazeProblem.getCost​(MazeState state)
      Returns cost of an action depending on the type of tile is for the current position The cost to move to a Goal state is 1 unit, the cost to move to an Initial state is 1 unit, the cost to move to a Mud tile is 3 units, the cost to move to a wall is not applicable, since it is not possible to move to a wall, and the cost to move to a Key state is 1 unit
